These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
City: hannover, nizza
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| City   | nizza | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
City: nizza, miami
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the person traveling to miami##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| City   | miami | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, apricot
1. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
3. the person who likes black is not to the right of the person who likes black##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Color   | black | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, september
1. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Birthday   | june | september |

 #################################

 
